like to share with you the development approach that can lead you to having an offline application

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:34.520
that is fully native and is using the R technology that you are using to build your models. So

00:10:34.520 --> 00:10:38.960
usually when you start with a simple R Shiny POC, you can iterate very quickly because

